is like, well, you knew--

33:40.433 --> 33:42.266
- He didn't say he was
a f---ing--

33:42.266 --> 33:43.533
Yeah, I know
exactly what you mean.

33:43.533 --> 33:44.667
I'm gonna miss Chris.

33:44.667 --> 33:46.433
I enjoyed his company.

33:46.433 --> 33:47.567
I mean, he never had
his heart in this,

33:47.567 --> 33:49.667
